dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Atlantic City, New Jersey (Title Sheet)
dct_description_sm: Includes key, streets and specials index, and text. "4031." North oriented towards upper right. Some sheets have photographs of Atlantic City tipped in; photograph on sheet 2 has caption title: General view of Atlantic City showing principal hotels & piers.
